(S, O,) or signifies also, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he affected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constrained himself, to abstain from what was unlawful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was patient, and kept himself remote,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aloof, from a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that was unlawful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani AlmasoA^alapi","text_ar":"عَنِ المَسْاَلَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstEf~","text_ar":"استعفّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he abstained"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaf~a","text_ar":"عَفَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from begging:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) whence the trad. of the Prophet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaEofifo Eani Als~uw^aAli maA A@sotaTaEota","text_ar":"اِسْتَعْفِفْ عَنِ السُّوَالِ مَا ا@سْتَطَعْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Abstain thou from begging, as much as thou art able"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAisotiEofaAfu","text_ar":"الاِسْتِعْفَافُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the seeking to abstain from what is unlawful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from begging of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani","text_ar":"عَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEtf~","text_ar":"اعتفّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqabiyHi","text_ar":"القَبِيحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he abstained from that which was evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; this being [likewise] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEif~apu","text_ar":"العِفَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaf~a","text_ar":"عَفَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of milk, aor"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaf~N","text_ar":"عَفٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It collected in the udder:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it remained in the udder;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) or thus"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaf~a fiY AlD~aroEi","text_ar":"عَفَّ فِى الضَّرْعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ibn-'Abbád, O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","M","TA","IDrd"]},{"entry_id":"n29700","headword_ar":"عَفٌّ","root":"Ef","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; and its fem.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EafyifN","text_ar":"عَفيِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}